\begin_layout Standard
This is an 
\series bold
open standard
\series default
.
 Any healthcare provider or app developer can deploy this technology.
 There are no licensing fees, patents, or other intellectual property barriers.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Any app will work with any healthcare provider.
 There is no need for each healthcare provider to create a dedicated app,
 although many healthcare providers may choose to do so.
 Users can choose the app that best fits their individual needs: for example,
 a niche app could be developed with a user interface designed for a particular
 visual impairment.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Healthcare providers can work independently or can choose to share notifications
 with selected other healthcare providers in order to maximise the worldwide
 effectiveness of contact tracing.
\end_layout

