\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
zero or more Downstream Publishers, and
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
zero or more Peer Publishers.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The hierarchy is expected to reflect a geographical relationship of the
 corresponding Subscription Zones:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The geographical Upstream Subscription Zone associated with the Upstream
 Publisher (if any) is expected to wholly contain the geographical Subscription
 Zone associated with the Publisher.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The geographical Downstream Subscription Zones associated with the Downstream
 Publishers (if any) are expected to be wholly contained by the geographical
 Subscription Zone associated with the Publisher.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The geographical Peer Subscription Zones associated with the Peer Publishers
 (if any) are expected to overlap with or adjoin the geographical Subscription
 Zone associated with the Publisher.
\end_layout

